{"tid":1829021,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"各位私了左自己藍絲老豆老母未","createTime":"2020-01-18T11:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T10:15:34.000Z","uid":43861,"like":80,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"781a8112b5fdea3338ccd384d27b4d28c9ae05ca","tid":1829021,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"話說陳晚我唱緊願榮光歸香港個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎叫我飲左佢<br />\n咁唱緊聖歌又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母呢個藍絲狗5分鐘入黎煩我一次<br />\n最後我頂唔撚順係佢面前倒晒佢碗湯落地下<br />\n跟住佢眼濕濕扮委屈咁拖返乾撻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗你一開始唔好咁煩咪得囉 你逼我飲我就係都唔飲呀你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我再將老豆啲相呀 馬報全部撕爛晒"},{"pid":"72f5d1f91507fd32103616e125751d1b694787bd","tid":1829021,"uid":35067,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"支持  不割"},{"pid":"e6a86ea5c7ba8933c921ca232e3163f435290174","tid":1829021,"uid":261505,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff76a4a98558b2efec7e4770b03dcd78005b03f","tid":1829021,"uid":243550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb7df1a3e6fffe431933fa9f74f09ed4f6a6898","tid":1829021,"uid":330582,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"我偷影左佢地大頭"},{"pid":"0480a616e0f5f6fad78f152475289ab523e6c92f","tid":1829021,"uid":242537,"like":0,"